# Incident Management Framework

A comprehensive incident management toolkit based on ITIL 4 principles and 10+ years of hands-on experience in IT operations and incident coordination.

## ðŸŽ¯ Overview

This framework provides standardized templates, procedures, and best practices for managing IT incidents from detection through resolution. Designed for organizations implementing or improving their incident management processes.

