## ðŸ“Š Incident Severity Classification

| Priority | Response Time | Resolution Target | Examples |
|----------|--------------|-------------------|----------|
| P1 - Critical | 15 minutes | 4 hours | Complete service outage |
| P2 - High | 1 hour | 8 hours | Major functionality impaired |
| P3 - Medium | 4 hours | 24 hours | Minor functionality affected |
| P4 - Low | 8 hours | 72 hours | Minimal impact, cosmetic issues |

